Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:24.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,《星际迷航: 新世界》前情提要\N{\rENG}Previously on Star Trek: Strange New Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,向在通讯范围内的所有联邦星舰求救\N{\rENG}To any Federation vessels in range, need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,遭遇戈恩人袭击\N{\rENG}Under attack by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,如今星际联邦和戈恩霸权的关系非常紧张\N{\rENG}The Federation's at a dangerous point in our relationship with the Gorn Hegemony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,这看起来像是一条分界线\N{\rENG}It looks like a demarcation line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:38.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,帕纳索斯贝塔星和他们所有的武装力量\N{\rENG}With Parnassus Beta and all their forces
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这条线的另一边\N{\rENG}on the far side of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:40.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 我认为我们的人\N{\rENG}Unfortunately, that is where
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:42.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,被关押在那里\N{\rENG}I believe our people are being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不打算丢下他们不管\N{\rENG}I don't plan on leaving them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我头脑里藏着的东西是拯救进取号的答案\N{\rENG}If somewhere in my head is the answer to saving the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我必须冒这个险\N{\rENG}then that's a risk I have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:52.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,拿着这个\N{\rENG}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,它能帮你藏起来\N{\rENG}It'll help you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rENG}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,在下蒙哥马利·斯考特\N{\rENG}Montgomery Scott at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:01.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么还活着\N{\rENG}How are you not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道如何隐藏在众目睽睽之下\N{\rENG}Well, I figured out how to hide in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你造了个戈恩人的应答器吗\N{\rENG}You built a Gorn transponder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,总的来说 对于扫描仪而言\N{\rENG}Eh, basically, to a scanner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的穿梭机看起来像是戈恩飞船\N{\rENG}the shuttle looked like a Gorn ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还能再造一个类似之前的设备吗\N{\rENG}Could you build another device like the one you made?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:11.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\rENG}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特尔舰长需要马上注射镇定剂\N{\rENG}Captain Batel is in need of immediate sedation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,昨天发生的\N{\rENG}Happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不会放弃她的\N{\rENG}I'm not giving up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:18.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也没那个打算\N{\rENG}I have no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 传送机目前在星球表面上未探测到任何人\N{\rENG}Captain, the transporter is not currently picking up anyone on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:29.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾普里尔上将命令我们马上撤离\N{\rENG}Admiral April's ordering our immediate withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,殖民地居民和外勤队\N{\rENG}The colonists and the landing party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,显然被传送到了\N{\rENG}appear to have been beamed up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:33.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的船上\N{\rENG}by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 请下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在 即将揭晓结局\N{\rENG}And now, the conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 请下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,护盾只剩50%了\N{\rENG}Shields at 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\rENG}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:13.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 请下令\N{\rENG}Orders, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉 再重复一下上将刚刚的命令\N{\rENG}Uhura, repeat April's last order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:16.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退 并且\N{\rENG}Retreat and rendez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退并与舰队汇合 舰长\N{\rENG}Retreat and rendezvous with the fleet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:20.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,他给了坐标\N{\rENG}He gave coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他没说要立即汇合 对吧\N{\rENG}But he didn't say immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,行了 各位有什么点子吗\N{\rENG}All right, who's got ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,声东击西\N{\rENG}Diversionary tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:27.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们被围困得太厉害了\N{\rENG}We're too boxed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,排空曲速舱 制造一片等离子云团?\N{\rENG}Vent the nacelles, create a cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们自己也看不见了\N{\rENG}We need to be able to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,干扰敌方的通讯\N{\rENG}Jam their comms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,使其无法协调攻击\N{\rENG}so they can't coordinate attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,对 就是这个\N{\rENG}That's it. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人使用光信号作为舰对舰通讯手段\N{\rENG}The Gorn use light for ship-to-ship messaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在调整偏导阵列来发射光谱\N{\rENG}I'm modulating the deflector array to emit a spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,应该能迷惑他们一阵\N{\rENG}Should confuse them for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 现在想想要怎么把自己人传送回来\N{\rENG}All right, now how do we beam our people back to Enterprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,扫描显示戈恩星舰能够阻断传送\N{\rENG}Scans indicate the Gorn ships are transport-resistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以即便我们绕过了护盾\N{\rENG}So, even if we get past the shields,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,也需要授权码才行\N{\rENG}we need authorization codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,没时间去破解密码了\N{\rENG}No time to hack codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,先撤再救\N{\rENG}Retreat and rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是一堆烂选项里最好的了\N{\rENG}It's the best of a bunch of bad options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们要怎样追踪一艘\N{\rENG}So how do we track this specific ship
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,跨越数光年的船呢\N{\rENG}across light-years of space?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,沃凯矿 一种稀有元素\N{\rENG}Wolkite. A rare element
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,含有子空间规范玻色子\N{\rENG}that contains subspace gauge bosons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们调整一个定位信标\N{\rENG}If we modified a homing beacon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人远远地就能看到信标飞过来\N{\rENG}The Gorn would see a beacon coming from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果是鱼雷就不会\N{\rENG}Not if it's a torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们对他们发射一颗哑弹\N{\rENG}We tag 'em with a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人猜不到我们要干什么\N{\rENG}The Gorn won't know what we're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,护盾只剩30%了\N{\rENG}Shields at 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,要想这个方法奏效 我们仍需穿透\N{\rENG}For this to succeed, we still need to penetrate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩星舰的护盾系统\N{\rENG}the Gorn's defensive systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们已经用上了所有武器攻击他们\N{\rENG}We've been hitting them with everything we've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,没多大用\N{\rENG}it doesn't do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,能量护盾基于谐波运作\N{\rENG}Uh, energy shields work on harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们找对频率\N{\rENG}If we find the right frequency...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以撞击敌舰\N{\rENG}We can ram the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的护盾和他们的接触时\N{\rENG}When our shields make contact with theirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,两列谐波叠加时会出现相消干涉现象\N{\rENG}they will create a destructive interference pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,并在短时间内中断这两个频率的护盾\N{\rENG}and momentarily interrupt both frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有护盾 我们就是活靶子\N{\rENG}With our shields down, we'd be sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们就只有一次机会\N{\rENG}We'd only have one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就足够了\N{\rENG}That's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 调转方向\N{\rENG}Mitchell, bring us around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,与敌方驱逐舰正面交火\N{\rENG}head-to-head with the destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,是时候来点硬碰硬了\N{\rENG}Time to play a game of chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,全舰注意 做好冲击准备\N{\rENG}All decks, prepare for impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,随时可让脉冲引擎全速推进 舰长\N{\rENG}Full impulse on your orders, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,让惯性阻尼器最大功率运行\N{\rENG}Inertial dampeners to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有人 抓稳扶好了\N{\rENG}Everybody hold onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:10.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,乌娜\N{\rENG}Una...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:12.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\rENG}let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,发射鱼雷\N{\rENG}Fire torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 曲速带离\N{\rENG}Helm, warp us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\rENG}On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,坚持住 各位\N{\rENG}Hang in there, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我们已到达汇合点\N{\rENG}Captain, we've arrived at the rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,联邦星舰巴勃罗·毕加索号在联络我们\N{\rENG}The USS Pablo Picasso is hailing to greet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:43.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,是艾普里尔上将 舰长\N{\rENG}It's Admiral April, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,他现在要传送上舰听取汇报\N{\rENG}He's beaming aboard now to debrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,还要打针吗\N{\rENG}More needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 得再来几针\N{\rENG}Yes, just a few more pokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有这些\N{\rENG}I mean, without these,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的身体会在静滞场里面坏死 所以\N{\rENG}your body will go necrotic in the stasis field, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你会变紫 会很难看\N{\rENG}Things turn purple. It's not pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我从没被冻结冬眠过\N{\rENG}I've never been frozen solid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,这前景不怎么激动人心\N{\rENG}It's not an exciting prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 等我们解决了这小小的戈恩卵感染问题\N{\rENG}Well, as soon as we work out this little Gorn infection,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就又能活蹦乱跳的了\N{\rENG}you'll be up and around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.86,Note,,0,0,0,,* 原文是指小说《瑞普·凡·温克尔》里主人公一觉睡了二十年 醒来发现世界已经天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,感觉我会像小说里瑞普那样 一醒来发现一切都变了\N{\rENG}So this could be like a Rip Van Winkle thing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得你更会像是睡美人\N{\rENG}I see you more as a Sleeping Beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着 我之前说的是认真的\N{\rENG}Listen, I meant what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦那时要在我和其他船员之间做出选择\N{\rENG}The moment it looks like me or the crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,就牺牲掉我\N{\rENG}you take me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,不要想这些了\N{\rENG}Don't think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,静滞状态会阻止你和戈恩胚胎\N{\rENG}Stasis will prevent you and the Gorn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,进行任何形式的细胞生长\N{\rENG}from any type of cellular growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,做好最坏的打算\N{\rENG}There's another side to the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论代价如何\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论代价如何 我保证\N{\rENG}Whatever it takes. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我现在要给你注射镇静剂了\N{\rENG}I'm, uh, I'm gonna give you a sedative now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你醒来 戈恩感染的问题就治好了\N{\rENG}And when you wake up, you will be Gorn-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,肾上腺素和中和剂 快\N{\rENG}Epinephrine and neutralizer, stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身体正在排斥血清\N{\rENG}Her body's rejecting the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,医务室呼叫舰桥\N{\rENG}Sickbay to bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,有个最新消息 情况不太乐观\N{\rENG}Uh, I have an update, and it's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,告诉我最坏情况\N{\rENG}Bottom line it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特尔舰长对低温血清过敏\N{\rENG}Captain Batel is allergic to cryoserum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不能把她放进静滞状态\N{\rENG}We can't put her in stasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,那她的生命已经进入倒计时了吗\N{\rENG}So she's back on a ticking clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,她身体里的戈恩卵会在\N{\rENG}The Gorn will hatch from her body in, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,一天之内孵化\N{\rENG}in less than a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我正在努力寻找治疗的方法\N{\rENG}I'm stuck trying to find a treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rENG}Um... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许如果约瑟夫在这里 就可以\N{\rENG}maybe if Joseph was here, I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会派人去帮忙\N{\rENG}I'm sending help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀\N{\rENG}Christine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\rENG}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,救救她\N{\rENG}Help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能 舰长\N{\rENG}I'll do my best, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:57.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我或许不是医生\N{\rENG}Captain, I may not be a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我能够把我所有的能力都奉献在巴特尔舰长的治疗上\N{\rENG}but I will dedicate all of my abilities to Captain Batel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,直到解决她的戈恩卵感染\N{\rENG}until her Gorn infection is... resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,就只是看着?\N{\rENG}Just stand by?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可是有一整支舰队在待命啊\N{\rENG}You have the entire fleet out there ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是力量展示\N{\rENG}It's a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们先要建立起有效的巡逻\N{\rENG}First we need to establish patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们真这么觉得吗\N{\rENG}Do they really think
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,觉得戈恩人只要炸完这些殖民地\N{\rENG}the Gorn are just gonna stop and go home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,就会收手然后回家?\N{\rENG}after they raided those colonies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:28.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 这是很棘手的情况\N{\rENG}Look, it's a tough situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我们必须一次解决一个问题\N{\rENG}but we have to manage it one piece at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,无数无辜生命正危在旦夕 鲍勃\N{\rENG}There are innocent lives at stake, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}And I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这件事发生在我们的管辖范围之外\N{\rENG}But it's happening outside of our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜托 鲍勃\N{\rENG}Oh, come on, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,除了你那不怕死的狗斗之外\N{\rENG}Apart from your reckless dogfight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些攻击和联邦并没有关系\N{\rENG}these attacks do not involve the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们有规定的 克里斯\N{\rENG}We have regulations, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 就因为死的不是联邦公民\N{\rENG}So, because it's non-Federation citizens that are dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们就作壁上观吗\N{\rENG}we do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们对于联邦成员国都有义务在身\N{\rENG}We have an obligation to our member worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,那可是数十亿人\N{\rENG}Billions of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在就贸然投入战争\N{\rENG}To rush into a fight right now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,会将所有人都置于危险当中\N{\rENG}puts all of them at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不能这样\N{\rENG}We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还没从克林贡战争中完全恢复\N{\rENG}We're still recovering from the Klingon War.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说得一点没错\N{\rENG}You are absolutely right,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩就是利用这一点发动进攻\N{\rENG}and the Gorn sense our weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们现在是猎物\N{\rENG}We are prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们只会把这条霸权的边境线\N{\rENG}They will push this Hegemony line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,向着联邦领空内部推得越来越深\N{\rENG}further and further into Federation space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也知道他们会这么做\N{\rENG}And you know they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,等到我们真的恢复过来\N{\rENG}And by the time we actually get around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,有精力反制的时候\N{\rENG}to doing something about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,一切就太晚了\N{\rENG}it'll be way too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我听说了外勤队的事\N{\rENG}I heard about the landing party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,对啊 还有几百号殖民地居民呢\N{\rENG}Yeah, and a couple hundred colonists, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,玛丽呢\N{\rENG}And Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在医务室里\N{\rENG}She's in sickbay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,官方地说 给你的命令是监控分界线\N{\rENG}Officially, your orders are to monitor the demarcation line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,避免戈恩人的进一步进犯\N{\rENG}for any encroachment by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,好 那不官方的呢\N{\rENG}Okay. And unofficially?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,为何不给他们点颜色看看 告诉他们我们不是猎物\N{\rENG}How do we punch back and show them we aren't prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,行 我接受这个\N{\rENG}Yeah, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做的这个装置\N{\rENG}This contraption of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,你再说一遍它是干什么的\N{\rENG}what's it supposed to do again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,发射极化电磁信号\N{\rENG}Emit a polarized EM signature that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,诱骗戈恩 让它们以为我们是他们中的一员\N{\rENG}tricks the Gorn into thinking we're one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,类似隐身装置的原理\N{\rENG}It's like a cloaking device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么它究竟是怎么做到这一点的\N{\rENG}And how, exactly, does it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,说实话 我不太记得了\N{\rENG}Ah, if I'm being honest, I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是当时灵机一动\N{\rENG}I was kind of in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,很好 那我现在要问一个很蠢的问题\N{\rENG}Well, now I'm going to ask a silly question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:18.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且我确定我知道答案\N{\rENG}to which I'm pretty sure I know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,别又来这个\N{\rENG}Not this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像回到了报告厅一样\N{\rENG}It's like being back in lecture hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道 你又没去过报告厅\N{\rENG}How would you know that? You were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我去过 在后排而已\N{\rENG}I was there, in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在把这堆东西拼起来时\N{\rENG}Did you record a work-in-progress log
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有记工作日志\N{\rENG}while you were jury-rigging this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,啥 您的意思是在戈恩人正在轰炸我的时候记录?\N{\rENG}What, you mean as the Gorn were tearing our ship apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯考特 工程学第一定律就是写下来\N{\rENG}First rule in engineering, Scotty: write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们被要求无论什么情况下\N{\rENG}There's a reason we track our work
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,都要记录自己的工作是有理由的\N{\rENG}no matter what the circumstance, and this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在的这个情况 就是最好的理由\N{\rENG}this right now, this is precisely the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉打断\N{\rENG}Pardon the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们还要多久能让这东西恢复运作\N{\rENG}How long before you get that working?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 派克舰长 问题是\N{\rENG}Oh, Captain Pike, the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,它在我的小穿梭机上能起作用\N{\rENG}it worked on my wee shuttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,但进取号就\N{\rENG}but the Enterprise is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,那您什么时候需要它呢 舰长\N{\rENG}How soon do you need it, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们正在航向戈恩的领空\N{\rENG}We're headed into Gorn space,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以现在能用就最好了\N{\rENG}so now would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,在我们跨过分界线之前它会准备好的\N{\rENG}It'll be up and working before we cross the Hegemony line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我希望如此 因为我和船上所有人的命都指望在它身上了\N{\rENG}I'm counting on it, as are the lives of everyone on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管有没有这个装置\N{\rENG}We're going after our missing crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们都要去搜救被抓走的船员\N{\rENG}with or without that device.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了吗\N{\rENG}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇 还真是一点压力都没有呢\N{\rENG}Well, that's no pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\rENG}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安 勇敢点\N{\rENG}La'An, be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,对危险没有畏惧之心才会置你于死地\N{\rENG}Not believing you're gonna die is what gets you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是戈恩人\N{\rENG}It's the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,醒醒\N{\rENG}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,快醒醒\N{\rENG}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,你能做到的\N{\rENG}You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,第一个倒霉的总是医生\N{\rENG}Always start with the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的妈 我的手\N{\rENG}Holy crap, my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我他妈的半只手都没了\N{\rENG}Half my hand is frickin' gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾丽卡 看着我\N{\rENG}Erica, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,看着我 冷静下来\N{\rENG}Look at me. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,会没事的\N{\rENG}It's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,只要我们能回到船上就能治好它\N{\rENG}We can fix this when we get back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\rENG}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,先保持冷静\N{\rENG}Try to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但怎么\N{\rENG}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们怎么才能回到船上\N{\rENG}How do we get back to the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且他们怎么办\N{\rENG}What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们一次只能解救一个人\N{\rENG}If we free them one at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我们能救出来的人屈指可数\N{\rENG}we'll only get a handful out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果能的话\N{\rENG}If that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,光是我们四个人脱困就花了这么久\N{\rENG}Look how long it took for the four of us to get loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是一个巨大的消化腔\N{\rENG}This is a massive digestive chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且它正在消化\N{\rENG}And it's working its way through...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,看起来像是燃料加工厂\N{\rENG}looks like a-a processing plant for fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者只是戈恩人的食物工厂\N{\rENG}Or just food for the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不想变成哪个戈恩人的盘中餐\N{\rENG}I don't like the idea of being anyone's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,即便我们能够唤醒他们\N{\rENG}And even if we can wake them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管是一个还是一百个\N{\rENG}one or a hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还是没法离开这个\N{\rENG}we still don't have a way out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不知道什么的地方\N{\rENG}wherever this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,先一步一步来吧\N{\rENG}One step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是什么都不做 就是等死\N{\rENG}Sitting here doing nothing is a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且搞不好\N{\rENG}And for all we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些戈恩人可能在我们醒来那会就被惊动了\N{\rENG}the Gorn were alerted the moment that we woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以那些杀人蜥蜴可能已经在来的路上了\N{\rENG}So the killer lizards could already be on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\rENG}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,别害怕\N{\rENG}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安\N{\rENG}La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么\N{\rENG}No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安\N{\rENG}La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 你在想什么\N{\rENG}What's on your mind, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\rENG}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅仅关乎我们自己\N{\rENG}It's not just about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些殖民地居民很快也会被杀害\N{\rENG}All of these people will be dead soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,看这\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,这看起来像个排泄桩\N{\rENG}This looks like an evacuation pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:10.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许 这艘船不能处理的东西 都由它排出\N{\rENG}Maybe whatever the ship can't process, it expels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,粪堆里的武器\N{\rENG}Weapons from a crap pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,怪了 这个方向是对的\N{\rENG}Strangely, it's a step in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想只救下屈指可数的人\N{\rENG}I don't want to save a handful of colonists,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:38.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想拯救全部人\N{\rENG}I want to save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有还活着的人 都能回家\N{\rENG}Everyone that's still alive gets home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,即使这意味着 我们必须杀出一条血路\N{\rENG}Even if we have to shoot our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你个蠢货\N{\rENG}Ack, bawheid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:14.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是这样\N{\rENG}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,是戈恩人 他们来了\N{\rENG}They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rENG}Oh, shite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们完蛋了 斯考提\N{\rENG}We're doomed. Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:19.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,不不不不\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们都死定了\N{\rENG}We're all gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\rENG}It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,快通知舰桥 把它加到护盾上\N{\rENG}Tell the bridge to patch it to the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么 太晚了吗\N{\rENG}What? Is it too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰桥呼叫科学实验室 你们进展如何了\N{\rENG}Bridge to science lab. What's the status down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们马上要进入戈恩领空了\N{\rENG}We're about to enter Gorn space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是狡猾\N{\rENG}Oh, you minx.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,已经在正常运行了 舰长\N{\rENG}It's up and running, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们现在就能把它加到护盾上\N{\rENG}We can patch it into the shields now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,好极了 派克完毕\N{\rENG}Excellent. Pike out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑\N{\rENG}That wasn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,明明就很有趣\N{\rENG}It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你差点害我心脏病发作\N{\rENG}You nearly gave me a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我那么做 是因为我了解你\N{\rENG}I did it 'cause I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你才不了解呢\N{\rENG}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,太了解了 平时闲得发慌的时候你就摆了\N{\rENG}Yes, with too much time on your hands, you fall apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,但要是有相位枪顶着你的头 你立刻精神百倍\N{\rENG}but put a phaser to your head and voilà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你管我这么多干嘛\N{\rENG}Why do you care what I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你防备太重了 斯考提\N{\rENG}You put up walls, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你太害怕承担风险了\N{\rENG}You're too afraid to take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我修好了你想让我修的东西\N{\rENG}I fixed what you wanted me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且你相当目无上级\N{\rENG}And you're insubordinate to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,准确来说你又不是我的上级\N{\rENG}Well, technically you're not my C.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在驭星号上牺牲了\N{\rENG}She went down on the Stardiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以离开了吗 长官\N{\rENG}May I be excused, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 斯考提\N{\rENG}Oh, Scotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我们正在接近戈恩霸权领空边境\N{\rENG}Approaching the Hegemony demarcation line now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:21.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,脱离曲速\N{\rENG}Drop us out of warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,开启斯考特的应答器\N{\rENG}Start Mr. Scott's transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,应答器?\N{\rENG}Transponder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亚说它更像是一个改装过的电磁脉冲发射器\N{\rENG}Pelia says it's more like a modified EM pulse emitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就说得通了\N{\rENG}Okay, then that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人肯定不使用光学数据\N{\rENG}The Gorn must not use optical data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们已经进化了\N{\rENG}They've evolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以他们一定依赖生物识别信息\N{\rENG}so they must rely on biometrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,热量和电磁信号\N{\rENG}heat and EM signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯 是时候看看这到底能不能成功了\N{\rENG}Well, time to see if it actually works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 它应该可以\N{\rENG}It should. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,除非哪个戈恩人突然决定看一眼窗外\N{\rENG}unless maybe one of them decides to look out a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 戈恩狩猎舰正在接近\N{\rENG}Captain, Gorn hunters approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,保持稳定航线\N{\rENG}Keep us steady and on course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前为止 我没看到任何窗户\N{\rENG}So far, I don't see any windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,它奏效了\N{\rENG}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,乌乎拉 我们还能接收到沃凯矿信标的信号吗\N{\rENG}Uhura, do we still have a signal from the wolkite beacon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 舰长\N{\rENG}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,信号很弱且在逐渐减弱 但它还在发射信号\N{\rENG}It's faint and getting weaker but still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,有关于他们去向的情报吗\N{\rENG}Any intel on where they're headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,一个未知的双星系统\N{\rENG}An uncharted binary star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,那里的恒星活动\N{\rENG}The stellar activity there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我们前所未见的\N{\rENG}is like nothing we've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 设置航线\N{\rENG}Helm, plot a course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 那个星系的辐射高得超出量表\N{\rENG}Captain, the radiation in that system is off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:38.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,到最后 我们只能使用脉冲引擎\N{\rENG}At a certain point, we can only use impulse engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,进取号的护盾也无法抵挡辐射了\N{\rENG}and our shields won't be able to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,了解 那我们快速行动\N{\rENG}Understood. We'll make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 曲速七级\N{\rENG}Mitchell, warp factor seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命 舰长\N{\rENG}Aye aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:54.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\rENG}Intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩卵的孵化进程大幅改变了她身体的生物化学结构\N{\rENG}The incubation has severely altered her biochemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身体现在依赖于戈恩的幼体\N{\rENG}Her body is now as dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像戈恩幼体依赖于她\N{\rENG}on the Gorn hatchlings as they are on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,完美的宿主 不可分割\N{\rENG}The perfect host, inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,你试过显微减瘤术了吗\N{\rENG}Have you tried microscopic debulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:07.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,模拟完毕\N{\rENG}Results completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我最后跑的一次模拟\N{\rENG}It's the last simulation I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡率为100%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我做的每一次模拟 结果全都一样\N{\rENG}That's the chorus of the day. It's every simulation I've run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,计算机 模拟显微减瘤术的情境\N{\rENG}Computer, run scenarios for microscopic debulking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,将注射扎多拉提取物纳入模拟变量中\N{\rENG}factoring for an infusion of Zadora extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在处理\N{\rENG}Processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,猎户星的街头毒品?\N{\rENG}An Orion street drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,实话说 这真是天才想法\N{\rENG}Actually, that's kind of brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,是你教会了我跳出框架去看\N{\rENG}You are the one who taught me to look outside of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,是「去思考」\N{\rENG}It's "think,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,但也差不多\N{\rENG}but close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,克莉丝汀\N{\rENG}Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你想谈谈\N{\rENG}I know you want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽量简短\N{\rENG}I will be brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是想为你离开前\N{\rENG}I simply want to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们之间的结局道个歉\N{\rENG}for the way things ended before you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我当时情绪有点失控\N{\rENG}I reacted poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Apology accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,原谅你了\N{\rENG}We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,失去你的念头\N{\rENG}The thought of losing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,深深困扰着我\N{\rENG}it affected me deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\rENG}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,事情变得复杂了\N{\rENG}This has gotten complicated,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不擅长应对复杂\N{\rENG}and I am not good at complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,而我还是要离开三个月\N{\rENG}And I am still going away for three months
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:13.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,去和罗杰·科尔比一起学习\N{\rENG}to study with Roger Korby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我回来 再看看我们的状态吧\N{\rENG}When I get back, let's just see where we are then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以你是想说\N{\rENG}So you are saying that perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许分开一段时间 对我们有好处吗\N{\rENG}some time apart might be good for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\rENG}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不是说\N{\rENG}But not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,作为我们俩的我们\N{\rENG}not like "us" us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是说\N{\rENG}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:37.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,作为两个个体的我们\N{\rENG}us as people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,请别做那些你觉得浪漫的事\N{\rENG}Please don't do something you think is romantic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,像是等我之类的\N{\rENG}like wait for me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,扎多拉提取物情境模拟完毕\N{\rENG}Zadora extract scenario completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:50.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡率为100%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论我们用什么方法\N{\rENG}No matter how we approach this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特尔的人类基因\N{\rENG}Batel's human DNA is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,都存在不足\N{\rENG}Inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她的身体进入休克状态\N{\rENG}Her body goes into shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,血压开始下降\N{\rENG}blood pressure drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后死亡\N{\rENG}And she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,哼 人类的身体始终有限\N{\rENG}Huh. Human physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果我们给她的基因帮点忙呢\N{\rENG}What if we gave her some help there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,你已经有主意了\N{\rENG}You have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,伊勒利亚人的基因\N{\rENG}Illyrian DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:15.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,乌娜的血液\N{\rENG}Una's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:16.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,基因使其可以实时抵抗感染\N{\rENG}it's designed to combat infections in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:19.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,一剂血清可以给巴特尔的免疫系统来一次大升级\N{\rENG}A plasma injection could provide a boost to Batel's immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能在不使其休克的前提下\N{\rENG}And we could attempt the surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:21.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,尝试进行手术了\N{\rENG}without her going into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样做违反规定\N{\rENG}It is against regulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,但能挽救她的生命\N{\rENG}but it could save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:28.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,计算机 模拟手术结果\N{\rENG}Computer, run scenario for surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:31.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,将注射伊勒利亚血清纳入模拟变量中\N{\rENG}factoring for a plasma transfusion from an Illyrian blood donor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:33.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,处理中\N{\rENG}Processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:35.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,你当时是怎么说的来着\N{\rENG}How did you put it once?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,有些规则就是用来打破的?\N{\rENG}Some rules are intended to be broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:42.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,几乎准确无误了\N{\rENG}Almost exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:43.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是机库\N{\rENG}There's the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:44.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家都了解计划吧\N{\rENG}Everyone's clear on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:48.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,访问这艘船的计算机主机\N{\rENG}Access the ship's mainframe,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,上传戈恩星舰的传送器密码\N{\rENG}upload the Gorn transporter codes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:52.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他们带回进取号\N{\rENG}Get them to the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:54.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,要成功 我们必须偷一艘飞船 从这里飞出去\N{\rENG}To do that, we have to steal a ship and fly it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:56.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个看起来没什么警戒措施\N{\rENG}That one doesn't look guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:22:59.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们超有把握 一点都不是不可能任务\N{\rENG}Totally got this, not impossible at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:02.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什么都能飞 是真的吧\N{\rENG}And it's true you can fly anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,别这么没礼貌 当然是真的\N{\rENG}Don't be rude. Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:07.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:08.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,来搞定那艘飞船吧\N{\rENG}Let's get to that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:11.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是个好计划\N{\rENG}This is a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,一定行得通\N{\rENG}It's gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:19.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是个好计划\N{\rENG}It's good. It's-it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.13,0:23:20.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,是个好计划 对吗\N{\rENG}It's a good plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\rENG}It's a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:25.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 我们现在只需要\N{\rENG}Yeah. Yeah. Now all we have to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:27.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,别被戈恩人逮住\N{\rENG}not get caught by the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:31.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,山姆\N{\rENG}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,你为啥要乌鸦嘴\N{\rENG}Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是姐们 这你也能怪我啊\N{\rENG}What? Oh, come on, you can't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:35.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,相位枪调到击杀档\N{\rENG}Phasers to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,该走了\N{\rENG}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:44.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和乌乎拉一直在钻研\N{\rENG}Uhura and I have been poring over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,手头能得到的戈恩人数据\N{\rENG}all available data on the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,确认的袭击 未被证实的目击\N{\rENG}Confirmed attacks, unverified sightings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:51.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果可能和戈恩人有关系 我们就检查过一遍\N{\rENG}If it might be a Gorn, we've checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:53.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,比我们想象的信息多出很多\N{\rENG}And there's a lot more out there than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:56.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你得稍微用点想象力\N{\rENG}You have to squint a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:57.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是每一次戈恩目击事件\N{\rENG}But every Gorn sighting correlates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,都和某个特定的恒星活动规律正相关\N{\rENG}to a pattern of specific stellar events.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,日冕物质抛射\N{\rENG}Coronal mass ejections.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经了解过了\N{\rENG}I know this already, CMEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:04.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,恒星耀斑爆发会引发强烈恒星风\N{\rENG}Stellar flares can set off a frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 其活动遵循一定的规律\N{\rENG}Yes, the attacks follow a pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:09.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的休眠也是如此\N{\rENG}but so does Gorn inactivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:11.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,这都是乌乎拉发现的\N{\rENG}Uhura is the one who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.44,0:24:12.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们知道有很长一段时间\N{\rENG}There are long periods of time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.79,0:24:14.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有任何戈恩人活动的报告\N{\rENG}where no Gorn activity is reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:16.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,甚至连一点风声都没有\N{\rENG}Not so much as a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:18.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,在那个时间段\N{\rENG}And in those instances,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,独特的恒星活动似乎触发了某些东西\N{\rENG}there's unique stellar activity that seems to trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,休眠\N{\rENG}Hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:22.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们认为戈恩人有着漫长的休眠周期\N{\rENG}We believe that the Gorn have a long hibernation cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:27.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,在适当的条件下 它们会变得温顺\N{\rENG}Under the right conditions, they become docile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.34,0:24:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以利用这一点\N{\rENG}We can use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:29.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的科学团队协助了计算\N{\rENG}The science team chipped in on the math
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:32.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功识别出X级太阳耀斑及其伴随的上弓下沉流\N{\rENG}and was able to isolate the presence of X-class flares
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:34.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,两者在消失前均有明显前兆\N{\rENG}and supra-arcade downflows that precede their absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,做的好 你们俩\N{\rENG}Good work, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:40.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,还有一点\N{\rENG}There's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,数据表明\N{\rENG}The data also suggests that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.20,0:24:47.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可能正处于戈恩人长期侵略行为的初期\N{\rENG}we could be at the beginning of a long cycle of Gorn aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:49.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,这些袭击可能预示着\N{\rENG}These attacks could signal what
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.58,0:24:52.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人即将发动全面入侵\N{\rENG}could soon be a full-scale Gorn invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:57.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我们将在两分钟后脱离曲速\N{\rENG}Dropping out of warp in two minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.36,0:24:59.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 米歇尔 我们这就来\N{\rENG}Thank you, Mitchell. On our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:12.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克和查普尔知道自己在做什么\N{\rENG}Spock and Chapel know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.12,0:25:13.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信他们\N{\rENG}I trust them
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.96,0:25:15.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,会好好利用我的血液\N{\rENG}with a couple liters of my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.08,0:25:19.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.25,0:25:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们说这可能是她唯一的机会\N{\rENG}They say it may be her only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:23.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,为了玛丽 他们需要什么我都愿意提供\N{\rENG}For Marie, they can take all they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.62,0:25:25.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,这次任务不留存记录\N{\rENG}This mission's already off-the-record,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以也没什么好报告的\N{\rENG}so nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.17,0:25:29.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.78,0:25:31.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,听一听你自己的建议吧\N{\rENG}take some of your own advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:34.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,要抱有希望\N{\rENG}Focus on hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.05,0:25:41.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,伊勒利亚血液供给方案已完成\N{\rENG}Illyrian blood donor scenario completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.48,0:25:45.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,死亡概率为86%\N{\rENG}Probability of fatality: 86%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:47.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有这个方案能让她有一线生机\N{\rENG}That's the first one that's given her any chance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.70,0:25:49.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,虽然成功率也不高\N{\rENG}Albeit not a very high one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.26,0:25:51.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,按理说 不能在这种概率下进行手术\N{\rENG}I mean, we can't do the surgery with these odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:54.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,但总算有所进展了 我们继续努力\N{\rENG}We're on to something. Let's keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.34,0:25:56.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:01.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们已接近辐射区\N{\rENG}We're near the radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.73,0:26:03.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,从现在起 只能使用脉冲引擎\N{\rENG}From here on, it's impulse engines only.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:11.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 你连续工作很久了\N{\rENG}Mitchell, you've been running nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.48,0:26:12.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,去换班吧\N{\rENG}Call for relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.58,0:26:14.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 在把所有人都救回来前\N{\rENG}With respect, I'm not leaving the station
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.57,0:26:16.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我绝不离开岗位\N{\rENG}until we get everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.53,0:26:18.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\rENG}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.31,0:26:21.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我收到了沃凯矿的信号\N{\rENG}I have the wolkite signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.32,0:26:30.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,即将接近敌方驱逐舰\N{\rENG}We're coming up on the enemy destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:31.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们多久能追上他们\N{\rENG}How soon can we overtake them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.20,0:26:32.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我们可能来晚了\N{\rENG}Chris, we may be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.46,0:26:33.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们已经进入了辐射区\N{\rENG}They've already entered the radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.89,0:26:35.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们继续深入当前星系\N{\rENG}If we go any deeper into this star system,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.84,0:26:37.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,全体船员都将陷入危险\N{\rENG}we put the entire crew at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.30,0:26:38.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,舵手 立即停船\N{\rENG}Helm, full stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:43.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,主屏幕切换为远距离观测画面\N{\rENG}Put the long-range visual up on the main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:49.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我的错觉 还是\N{\rENG}Is it me, or does it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.25,0:26:51.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,那艘船确实正朝着恒星的方向行驶?\N{\rENG}that ship is going to fly right into that star?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.18,0:26:54.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也看到了 简直难以置信\N{\rENG}I see it, I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.88,0:26:57.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,遥测数据已确认 舰长\N{\rENG}Telemetry confirms, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:26:58.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们必须做点什么\N{\rENG}We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.62,0:26:59.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\rENG}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:03.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们是失去动力了吗\N{\rENG}Did they just lose power?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.05,0:27:06.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.23,0:27:08.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我认为他们是故意的\N{\rENG}I think it was intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.53,0:27:10.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,但为什么呢\N{\rENG}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,将全部备用能量传输至护盾\N{\rENG}All auxiliary power to the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:22.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,尽可能争取在辐射区停留的时间\N{\rENG}Give me as much time as possible inside that radiation zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.06,0:27:24.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们追上去\N{\rENG}We're going after 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.25,0:27:32.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,新一轮日冕物质抛射活动逼近\N{\rENG}We've got another CME flare coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,她快不行了\N{\rENG}She's coding.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:41.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩幼体正在孵化\N{\rENG}The Gorn hatchlings are activating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.46,0:27:44.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,有什么东西加速了它们的生长\N{\rENG}Something has accelerated their growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.20,0:27:46.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,14%的成功率总比注定的死亡要好\N{\rENG}A 14% chance of survival is better than certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.46,0:27:50.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,准备手术吧\N{\rENG}Let's prep her for surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.60,0:28:01.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还能接收到沃凯矿的信号\N{\rENG}I'm still getting a ping on the wolkite signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.38,0:28:03.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们必须尽我们所能拯救我们的船员\N{\rENG}We need to get to our people while we still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.02,0:28:07.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里的磁场干扰让导航系统无法运作\N{\rENG}The magnetic fields here make navigation impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.25,0:28:09.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就解释了戈恩星舰为何会像失去动力一样\N{\rENG}That explains why the Gorn go into a free fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.60,0:28:12.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们利用了强重力井来完成大部分机动\N{\rENG}They let the intense gravity wells do most of the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:14.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,星际舰队方面没有回复\N{\rENG}No response from Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.47,0:28:16.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是因为这些辐射\N{\rENG}It's all the radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.30,0:28:17.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论是进取号还是双星系统以外的区域\N{\rENG}And no visuals on the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.88,0:28:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,都无法获得影像反馈\N{\rENG}or what's beyond the binary stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,这种光线折射方式会生成一种自然全息投影\N{\rENG}The light bends in a way that creates a natural hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.91,0:28:25.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦穿过它 就无法被看到了\N{\rENG}They're essentially invisible once they pass through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.31,0:28:27.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,形成了绝佳的防御屏障\N{\rENG}Makes for a great defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:29.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许那是一种降落程序\N{\rENG}Maybe it's a landing sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.01,0:28:30.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,有没有可能 戈恩母星就在这\N{\rENG}Could this be the Gorn homeworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.71,0:28:34.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果假设成立 那这就是他们回母星的方法\N{\rENG}If it is, that's how they go back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.71,0:28:38.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\rENG}Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.60,0:28:39.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,外面有情况\N{\rENG}something's moving out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:40.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,屏显\N{\rENG}On screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.36,0:28:55.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,一号\N{\rENG}Number One.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.17,0:29:05.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我计算了他们的轨迹\N{\rENG}I've plotted their trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.72,0:29:07.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些舰船正径直驶向联邦领空\N{\rENG}Those ships are headed straight for Federation territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.83,0:29:08.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,警告星际舰队\N{\rENG}Warn Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.90,0:29:10.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,只能使用深空通讯中继联络\N{\rENG}It's a deep space relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.44,0:29:12.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我无法确实他们是否收到了讯息\N{\rENG}I won't be able to confirm if they receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.14,0:29:13.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\rENG}We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.28,0:29:14.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,离开该星系的干扰范围\N{\rENG}Get clear of this system's interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 如果我们现在失去沃凯矿的信号\N{\rENG}Captain, if we lose our lock on the wolkite signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:18.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我无法保证我们能再次进行追踪\N{\rENG}I'm not sure we can reestablish contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.64,0:29:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们会失去外勤小队和殖民地居民\N{\rENG}We'll lose the landing party and the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.45,0:29:26.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以放置一个远程通信浮标\N{\rENG}We can drop a long-range communication buoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.46,0:29:27.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,将信号连接到浮标上\N{\rENG}Tie a signal to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:29.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,这样我们回来时就能找到他们了\N{\rENG}That way we can come back for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.63,0:29:32.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是我能想到的最好办法了\N{\rENG}It's the best I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:34.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,就这么做\N{\rENG}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们必须阻止这场入侵\N{\rENG}We have to stop this invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:38.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,通信浮标已部署\N{\rENG}Communication buoy is deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.82,0:29:40.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 持续锁定敌方舰队\N{\rENG}Mitchell, stay on that enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.60,0:29:41.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,调转舰艏\N{\rENG}Bringing her about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.70,0:29:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,尽快曲速离开这里\N{\rENG}As soon as we can, you warp out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.56,0:29:45.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,全速前进 直到我们能够将警报发给星际舰队\N{\rENG}Full throttle until we can alert Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.30,0:29:49.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在我们是联邦唯一的指望了\N{\rENG}We're the only hope the Federation's got right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.34,0:30:03.04,Note,,0,0,0,,* 此处查普尔和史波克穿的防护服与《原初系列》1x06 “The Naked Time” 中穿着的防护服是同一样式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.46,0:29:59.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,计算机 启动隔离模式\N{\rENG}Computer, engage quarantine mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.30,0:30:02.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,隔离模式已启动\N{\rENG}Quarantine mode engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:20.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果失败的话 这就是法雷奥贝塔的悲剧重演\N{\rENG}If this goes sideways, it's, it's Valeo Beta all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:20.16,Note,,0,0,0,,* 见《奇异新世界》1x09 联邦星舰游隼号上爆发戈恩寄生疫情 坠毁在法雷奥贝塔五星
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.29,0:30:22.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩卵疫情在全舰爆发的可能性将会是\N{\rENG}The probability of a full-scale Gorn outbreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.73,0:30:24.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不想知道\N{\rENG}I really don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.08,0:30:33.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普尔护士 联邦星舰进取号\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel, USS Enterprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.22,0:30:37.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,向患者巴特尔注射\N{\rENG}...injecting Patient Batel
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.35,0:30:40.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,实验性血浆溶液\N{\rENG}with experimental plasma solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.04,0:30:47.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,有进展吗 少尉\N{\rENG}Anything, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,通讯仍受阻碍 舰长\N{\rENG}Still jammed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.54,0:30:50.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人正在发送干扰信号\N{\rENG}The Gorn are transmitting an interference signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.20,0:30:55.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,距我们离开双星系统进入曲速还有多久\N{\rENG}How long before we clear these binary stars and go to warp?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.07,0:30:56.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,时间不够\N{\rENG}Not soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:58.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩星舰的航速比我们快得多\N{\rENG}Those Gorn ships are moving a lot faster than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:30:59.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,等警告发出\N{\rENG}By the time we get a signal out,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:01.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩舰队已经到达联邦外围成员国的位置了\N{\rENG}the Gorn will be right on top of the outer Federation worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:03.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们只能坐以待毙\N{\rENG}They're sitting ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.94,0:31:06.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,米歇尔 我们在戈恩舰队的武器射程内吗\N{\rENG}Mitchell, are we in shooting distance of the Gorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.32,0:31:10.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要让进取号对阵整个戈恩舰队吗\N{\rENG}Enterprise against an entire armada?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:12.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们根本不是对手\N{\rENG}We wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:25.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克呼叫科学实验室\N{\rENG}Pike to science lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.64,0:31:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亚 我需要你到舰桥来\N{\rENG}Pelia, I need you on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.18,0:31:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 舰长 马上来\N{\rENG}Aye, Captain, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.06,0:31:32.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么\N{\rENG}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.50,0:31:35.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和乌乎拉\N{\rENG}You and Uhura,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.80,0:31:37.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们之前说恒星耀斑决定了\N{\rENG}you said stellar flares can dictate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.76,0:31:40.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人的狩猎和休眠周期\N{\rENG}a Gorn's hunting and resting cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.46,0:31:41.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,确实如此\N{\rENG}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.86,0:31:43.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们甚至知道哪种辐射信号\N{\rENG}We even know precisely what kind of radiation signature
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.77,0:31:45.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,可以让戈恩人陷入休眠\N{\rENG}would tell the Gorn to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:48.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 这只是理论上的\N{\rENG}Um, sir, that's just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:51.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rENG}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.10,0:31:54.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们只需要人为制造一场恒星耀斑爆发\N{\rENG}...we just need to create a stellar flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:56.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉打断您 舰长\N{\rENG}Oh, forgive me for interrupting,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.02,0:31:57.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我们基本没办法对恒星造成什么影响\N{\rENG}but you cannot make a star do much of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,更别说是精确控制耀斑爆发了\N{\rENG}Certainly not precisely, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.80,0:32:01.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我们需要自己成为一次日冕物质抛射\N{\rENG}Which is why we need to become a CME, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.09,0:32:03.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,也就是X级耀斑\N{\rENG}X-flare ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.27,0:32:06.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 你看\N{\rENG}Captain, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:07.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你介意腾位置吗\N{\rENG}Uh, sorry, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯是 用星舰来操作\N{\rENG}Eh, sure, using the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.30,0:32:12.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,的确能让我们精准调控发射的辐射和电磁信号\N{\rENG}would allow us to modulate the exact radiation and EM signals we'd emit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.50,0:32:14.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你说的基本上就是\N{\rENG}But you're basically talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.41,0:32:16.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,把整艘船变成一颗人造恒星\N{\rENG}turning the ship into an artificial star.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:17.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,这基本上是不可能的\N{\rENG}That's-that's nearly impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.71,0:32:19.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,但并非完全不可能\N{\rENG}But not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.06,0:32:21.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,为了达到这个目的 我们必须深入到\N{\rENG}To do that, we'd have to go deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.34,0:32:23.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个致死的辐射区里\N{\rENG}into this deadly radiation zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.66,0:32:25.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,径直飞过外面那对双星之间\N{\rENG}fly right between those binary stars out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.94,0:32:29.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,想办法制造一个对抗磁场\N{\rENG}and create some kind of competing magnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.25,0:32:31.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,将粒子从双星中引开\N{\rENG}to draw particles away from both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.60,0:32:34.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,需要调整偏导护盾 通讯阵列 还有\N{\rENG}Modify the deflector shields, comms array, and, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:36.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,基本上系统都得重改一遍\N{\rENG}every-everything else, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.99,0:32:39.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,连舰体都要磁化 才能吸引恒星物质\N{\rENG}Magnetize the hull to attract stellar material.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.82,0:32:41.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,成功的几率是千分之一\N{\rENG}It's one in a thousand we'd get it done right
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.65,0:32:43.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,要么能完成任务要么炸飞自己 看吧\N{\rENG}or don't blow ourselves up along the way, and, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.96,0:32:50.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不确定 但我愿意赌一把\N{\rENG}Yeah, I don't know. I like those odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.88,0:32:53.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们就\N{\rENG}We'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:55.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,在爆炸前把它关闭\N{\rENG}...turn it off before we blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,就这么办\N{\rENG}Get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.80,0:33:04.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,患者对输血反应良好\N{\rENG}Patient is responding favorably to the transfusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:07.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,准备进行第一次手术切口\N{\rENG}Ready to make the first incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.36,0:33:42.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.85,0:33:50.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道最坏的情况是巴特尔舰长会殉职\N{\rENG}You know the most likely outcome is the death of Captain Batel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.07,0:33:52.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们只是需要一点信心\N{\rENG}We just have to have a little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.76,0:33:55.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,或许我们是从错误的角度来看待这件事的\N{\rENG}Perhaps we are looking at this from the wrong perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.44,0:33:58.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,与其在治疗巴特尔上花时间\N{\rENG}Instead of operating on Batel,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.58,0:34:00.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是我们试着去对付一下戈恩人呢\N{\rENG}what if we treated the Gorn inside of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.18,0:34:02.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,它们想要孵化出来觅食\N{\rENG}We know they emerge to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.40,0:34:03.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是我们给它们喂食呢\N{\rENG}What if we feed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.00,0:34:08.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它们喂饱 防止它们孵化\N{\rENG}Satiate them to keep them from coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.52,0:34:11.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,当他们不再处于攻击状态时 把它们干掉\N{\rENG}And when they are no longer in defensive mode, dissolve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.58,0:34:13.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,并用乌娜的伊勒利亚血浆\N{\rENG}And use Una's Illyrian plasma
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.57,0:34:15.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,来对抗他们在重新吸收过程中\N{\rENG}to fight the multitude of infections that will result
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.44,0:34:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,产生的大量感染\N{\rENG}from their reabsorption.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.72,0:34:17.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:21.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我们没有时间再去模拟一次了\N{\rENG}But we don't have enough time to run another simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.52,0:34:23.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像你刚才提议的那样\N{\rENG}As you suggested,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:24.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许我们只是需要一点信心\N{\rENG}perhaps we just need a little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.30,0:34:47.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们甩掉他们了吗\N{\rENG}Did we lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.47,0:34:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,或许吧\N{\rENG}Maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.14,0:34:51.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,即便甩掉了 也是暂时的\N{\rENG}but if so, then not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.13,0:34:54.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,这是个接口\N{\rENG}This is an interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.48,0:34:56.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,在戈恩的繁殖星球上\N{\rENG}They had them on the Gorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.92,0:34:58.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,也有这样的装置\N{\rENG}the Gorn breeding planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:02.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我哥哥马努 他\N{\rENG}My brother Manu, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.32,0:35:06.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,别害怕\N{\rENG}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.34,0:35:08.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,无论如何 别停下来\N{\rENG}Keep moving, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.98,0:35:09.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.30,0:35:15.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rENG}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.68,0:35:23.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你现在在这里 而不是在过去的那个地方\N{\rENG}You're here now, not back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.99,0:35:27.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 但这里也没好到哪去 不是吗\N{\rENG}Yeah, but here's not great either, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.38,0:35:30.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 确实很糟糕\N{\rENG}No, I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:38.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有印象了 让我试试看\N{\rENG}I remember. Let me try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.32,0:36:02.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\rENG}This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.06,0:36:05.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很想把这个拆开 弄明白它是怎么运作的\N{\rENG}I'd love to take this apart, figure out how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:06.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,真是好主意\N{\rENG}Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.48,0:36:07.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,在这待上一天慢慢研究吧\N{\rENG}Let's make a whole day of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.64,0:36:09.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,吃点零食 在这闲逛\N{\rENG}Get snacks, hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.22,0:36:12.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些看起来像是缓冲信号\N{\rENG}Those look like buffer signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.64,0:36:16.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 还有传送授权码\N{\rENG}They are. And the transport codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.26,0:36:19.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我们能把这个送回进取号\N{\rENG}If we can get this to the Enterprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.17,0:36:20.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,就能救走殖民地的居民\N{\rENG}then we can save the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.48,0:36:23.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,拯救所有人\N{\rENG}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.66,0:36:27.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,大伙们\N{\rENG}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:56.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,快去船上\N{\rENG}Get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.64,0:37:38.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们就位了\N{\rENG}We are in position,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.58,0:37:40.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在接近双星\N{\rENG}approaching the binary stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.96,0:37:43.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,当我们关闭电磁脉冲发生器的瞬间\N{\rENG}The moment we shut down the EM emitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:46.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,每一艘戈恩星舰都会直奔我们而来\N{\rENG}every single Gorn ship is going to come at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.22,0:37:47.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像飞蛾扑火一样\N{\rENG}Like moths to a flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.69,0:37:49.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,这也正是我们想要的效果\N{\rENG}Which is exactly what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.06,0:37:52.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家准备好了吗\N{\rENG}Everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.53,0:38:02.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,像太阳一般闪耀吧\N{\rENG}Make us shine like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.30,0:38:33.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,驾驶位\N{\rENG}The pilot seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.70,0:38:35.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,让我坐驾驶位\N{\rENG}Put me in the pilot seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.26,0:38:36.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来驾驶它\N{\rENG}Put me in the pilot seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.40,0:38:37.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,别逞强了\N{\rENG}Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.66,0:38:39.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能让它飞起来 这非我不可\N{\rENG}I can fly it. It has to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.88,0:38:41.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,她说得对 我们必须得离开这\N{\rENG}She's right. We need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:56.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们完全暴露在β粒子和伽马射线中了\N{\rENG}We're covered in beta particles and gamma rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.52,0:39:58.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,星舰正在承受着临界水平的辐射\N{\rENG}This ship is hitting critical levels of radiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.24,0:40:00.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人在做什么\N{\rENG}What are the Gorn doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.02,0:40:00.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们已经脱离编队\N{\rENG}They have broken ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.96,0:40:03.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前正处于进取号的拦截航线上\N{\rENG}currently on intercept course with Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.05,0:40:04.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前看起来一切顺利\N{\rENG}All right, so far, so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:05.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在看看它们会不会向我们开火\N{\rENG}Now let's see if they shoot at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.75,0:40:11.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我收到了一个\N{\rENG}Captain, I have a signal bouncing off
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.19,0:40:12.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,通讯信标反射的信号\N{\rENG}the communications beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.62,0:40:14.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,是拉安 长官\N{\rENG}It's La'An, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.45,0:40:18.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,进取号 能收到吗\N{\rENG}Enterprise, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.42,0:40:19.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安 你在哪\N{\rENG}La'An, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.32,0:40:20.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,在路上 如果能收到信号的话\N{\rENG}On our way. If you can read me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.59,0:40:22.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,注意接收我向你们发送的传送密码\N{\rENG}I'm sending you transport codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.20,0:40:23.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,把帕纳索斯人传送出去\N{\rENG}Beam the Parnassians out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.77,0:40:25.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们正在尝试传送\N{\rENG}We're trying to beam you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.74,0:40:26.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我们难以锁定你们\N{\rENG}but we're having trouble getting a lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:28.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们收到了吗\N{\rENG}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:30.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,它们正冲着我们来\N{\rENG}They're gaining on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.72,0:40:32.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,进取号 你们是否收到\N{\rENG}Enterprise, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.08,0:40:33.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,把帕纳索斯人传送回舰\N{\rENG}Beam the Parnassians out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.58,0:40:58.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 舰体完整性即将逼近极限\N{\rENG}Captain, hull integrity is approaching critical failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:13.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它关掉 关掉它\N{\rENG}Turn it off. Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.78,0:41:22.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,起作用了吗\N{\rENG}Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.35,0:41:26.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 舰长 最后一艘戈恩船只已返回母星\N{\rENG}Aye, sir, the last of the Gorn have gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.06,0:41:28.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,帕纳索斯人呢\N{\rENG}What about the Parnassians?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:29.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们及时把他们传回来了吗\N{\rENG}Did we get them out in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.74,0:41:31.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 舰长\N{\rENG}Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.38,0:41:33.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安的传送密码生效了\N{\rENG}The transport codes from La'An worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.62,0:41:35.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,几百名殖民地居民已经被救回\N{\rENG}Several hundred colonists accounted for
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.32,0:41:37.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在送往应急医务室\N{\rENG}and headed for the overflow infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:40.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我们急需--\N{\rENG}Captain, we need immediate as--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.18,0:41:42.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,将我们传送上舰并让一个医疗小组待命\N{\rENG}Beam us out and have a medical team standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.64,0:41:46.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克呼叫轮机部\N{\rENG}Pike to Engineering?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.14,0:41:48.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,是 舰长 我们正在使用传送码\N{\rENG}Aye, Captain, we're using the transport codes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.11,0:41:49.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,破解戈恩狩猎舰的系统\N{\rENG}to hack into the Gorn hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.86,0:41:51.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,应该很快就能搞定\N{\rENG}should be just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.64,0:41:54.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我们做到了\N{\rENG}Chris. Chris, we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:57.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们引起了戈恩人的长时休眠\N{\rENG}We triggered a long hibernation in the Gorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:41:58.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.70,0:42:00.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我忍不住在想\N{\rENG}But I can't help wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.88,0:42:03.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们会不会只是把麻烦推给了未来的人们\N{\rENG}if we didn't just create a problem for someone else to solve later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:08.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,舰长 我收到了艾普里尔上将的加密呼叫\N{\rENG}Captain. I'm getting a secure channel from Admiral April.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.65,0:42:09.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,接通\N{\rENG}Put him through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.74,0:42:14.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我们刚收到你的优先级讯息\N{\rENG}Chris. We just got your priority message.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.35,0:42:16.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,在戈恩舰队到这之前我们还有多少时间\N{\rENG}How much time do we have before the Gorn ships get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.38,0:42:17.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,请忽略最后一条讯息\N{\rENG}Ignore last transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.83,0:42:19.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少在一段时间内我们见不着戈恩人\N{\rENG}We won't be seeing the Gorn, at least not for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.06,0:42:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你有几分把握\N{\rENG}How certain are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.82,0:42:23.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 我已经对戈恩人还以颜色了\N{\rENG}Let's just say I found a way to punch back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.59,0:42:39.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,保持清醒 别晕过去\N{\rENG}Stay with me. Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.80,0:42:44.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我做的很棒\N{\rENG}I did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.69,0:42:45.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\rENG}Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:49.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,别说话了 你能撑住的\N{\rENG}Stop. You're going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.58,0:42:54.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,想干掉我 他们还不够格\N{\rENG}They'll have to try harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.39,0:42:59.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可是艾丽卡·奥特加斯\N{\rENG}I'm Erica Ortegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.27,0:43:00.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,无敌舵手\N{\rENG}I fly the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.16,0:43:02.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,撑住 有我在呢\N{\rENG}Hold on. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.94,0:43:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们尽力了\N{\rENG}We did all we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.64,0:43:22.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在要看巴特尔舰长自己了\N{\rENG}It's in Captain Batel's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.47,0:43:24.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,的确\N{\rENG}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.52,0:43:32.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.82,0:43:36.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有你的话 我没法做到这一切\N{\rENG}I couldn't have done that without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:37.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,不用谢\N{\rENG}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.97,0:43:54.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,她怎么样了\N{\rENG}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在实验室里 仍在恢复中\N{\rENG}She's in the lab, still in recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.25,0:44:11.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,外勤队已经救回\N{\rENG}Landing Party accounted for and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.84,0:44:13.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在应急医务室中接受治疗\N{\rENG}getting treatment in the overflow infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.60,0:44:15.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾丽卡伤得很重\N{\rENG}Erica is critical...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.30,0:44:16.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,但目前稳定\N{\rENG}but stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的通知\N{\rENG}Thanks for the update.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.13,0:44:21.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦我们离开辐射区域\N{\rENG}Once we clear the radiation bands,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.66,0:44:22.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,就设定航线回地球 曲速回家\N{\rENG}chart a course for Earth. Warp us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.87,0:44:25.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命 一号完毕\N{\rENG}Of course. Number One out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.56,0:44:56.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.82,0:44:59.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 主\N{\rENG}Okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.33,0:45:01.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,你赢了\N{\rENG}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.36,0:45:11.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\rENG}Our Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.97,0:45:13.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,在天上的主\N{\rENG}who art in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.36,0:45:14.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:17.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你醒了\N{\rENG}You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.78,0:45:21.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我想这意味着\N{\rENG}Yeah. Which I assume means
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.10,0:45:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些小戈恩们还没破肚而出\N{\rENG}that tiny Gorn didn't pop out of my body
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:25.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,杀了大家呢\N{\rENG}and kill everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:26.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.52,0:45:30.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然没有 我们都好好的呢\N{\rENG}No, no, no. We're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.98,0:45:32.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克和查普尔想出了治疗方案\N{\rENG}Spock and Chapel came up with a treatment, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.94,0:45:35.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,我后面会让他们解释给你听\N{\rENG}I'll have them walk you through it later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.38,0:45:39.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你还没有完全脱离危险\N{\rENG}...you're still not out of the woods yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.47,0:45:41.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的\N{\rENG}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.74,0:45:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,乌娜帮的忙\N{\rENG}Una helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.00,0:45:48.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 你就不应该那么做\N{\rENG}Chris, you shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.61,0:45:51.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,玛丽 我已经失去了太多 好吗\N{\rENG}Marie, I've already lost too much, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.69,0:45:54.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我们可以继续争\N{\rENG}So we can sit here and we can argue about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.01,0:45:55.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,争论未来会不会发生什么\N{\rENG}what might or might not happen in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.97,0:45:58.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,但能不能把那些都放一边 让我抱着你\N{\rENG}or you can just set all that aside and let me hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.63,0:46:05.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的不能再失去你\N{\rENG}I really don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.50,0:46:15.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rENG}I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.34,0:46:20.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还在呢\N{\rENG}I'm still here.
